 <name>Horde_Cache</name>
 <channel>pear.horde.org</channel>
 <summary>Horde Caching API</summary>
 <description>This package provides a simple, functional caching API, with the option to store the cached data on the filesystem, in one of the PHP opcode cache systems (APC, eAcclerator, XCache, or Zend Performance Suite&apos;s content cache), memcached, or an SQL table.</description>
